<span class='spoilerAnswerText'>
<a class="jsShowSpoiler spoilerAction">(view spoiler)</a><span class="spoilerContainer" style="display: none">[So I m confused about some of the storyline.<br />They killed Linda when they were about 21, and Henry killed Rachel about 4 years prior to current story.<br />Corbin is 35, so nothing from Henry in those 10 years and suddenly he is angry abt Corbin leaving him 10 years later n decides to teach Corbin a lesson by killing Rachel ? Did I miss some? <a class="jsHideSpoiler spoilerAction">(hide spoiler)</a>]</span>
</span>
</div>
