<div class='allCommunityAnswers'>
<div class='communityAnswer'>
<div class='communityAnswerBody'>
<div class='answererUserIcon'>
<a class="leftAlignedImage userPhoto" href="/user/show/87977114-tiarli-santello"><img alt="" src="https://s.gr-assets.com/assets/nophoto/user/u_100x100-259587f1619f5253426a4fa6fb508831.png" /></a>
</div>
<div class='communityAnswerTextContainer'>
<span class='communityAnswererName'>
<a href="/user/show/87977114-tiarli-santello">Tiarli Santello</a>
</span>
<span class='communityAnswerText'>
<div class='spoiler'>
This answer contains spoilers…
<span class='spoilerAnswerText'>
<a class="jsShowSpoiler spoilerAction">(view spoiler)</a><span class="spoilerContainer" style="display: none">[
  
    They killed Claire Brennan in college together, they thought it was best for them to not talk to each other and ran into each other later where they d<a href="#" rel="nofollow noopener">…more</a>
    They killed Claire Brennan in college together, they thought it was best for them to not talk to each other and ran into each other later where they decided to kill Linda. However Corbin, unlike Henry, isn't a psychopath so Corbin calls Henry saying he wants out. Henry has shown significant details of his like to stalk people and mentioned that he stalked Corbin. Within that time period, Corbin hadn't been with other girls and Rachel happened to be the first girl since Linda hence why Henry killed her. In a way, Henry can't stand the thought of Corbin leaving him and his passion murdering girls bring them together in Henry's mind. By killing his girlfriends he is telling Corbin that he is always watching and that he is always with Corbin, and because Corbin doesn't like murdering people and Henry doesn't believe that he kills the girls and mutilate them telling Corbin he in a way killed them too. <a href="#" rel="nofollow noopener">(less)</a>
  
 <a class="jsHideSpoiler spoilerAction">(hide spoiler)</a>]</span>
</span>
</div>
</span>
</div>
