<span id="freeTextContainer12518298446477825052">I finished this book last night and prepared a review in my head. This morning, I think I&apos;m just going to say I thought the book was contrived. It had some plot elements that were too convenient, some things that were just too implausible to be believed, and then rehashed the story from a different character&apos;s viewpoint. And I&apos;ll let it go at that.</span>
  <span id="freeText12518298446477825052" style="display:none">I finished this book last night and prepared a review in my head. This morning, I think I'm just going to say I thought the book was contrived. It had some plot elements that were too convenient, some things that were just too implausible to be believed, and then rehashed the story from a different character's viewpoint. And I'll let it go at that.</span>
